---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="月度深度" lang="zh">

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">月度深度</h1>
  <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-8">每月初发布：策略回测数据 + 经典案例精析 + 季节性分析。</p>
  <div class="card p-8 text-center">
    <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)] max-w-md mx-auto">首篇月度深度将在完成一个月每日研判后发布。</p>
  </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>
